Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「いま！」という　この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}なんだって　音楽に　出来たらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}まだ　全力で　やり切ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悔し涙　拭ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春のフレージング
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡が　努力の　先にあるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}限界は　あたしが決める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一回　大げさな夢を　探しにいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止めない　勇気こそ　強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何百回　挑戦かさねて　ここまで来た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}チャンスの神様　みててね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}離したくないメロディ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}輝きに変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いよ　届け…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「此时此刻」的这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.40,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望能以音乐将其铭刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:44.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还未拼尽全力到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断拭去的悔恨泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是青春的分句
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:55.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是努力之后便会有奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:01.15,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那极限由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:10.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次去追寻那庞大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:13.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}强大就是永不放弃的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:20.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}经历数百次的挑战　来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:24.97,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请机会之神看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.55,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不想忘记的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不愿放开的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:33.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变为耀眼的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:38.28,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将这份心意　传递出去…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------EDCN---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:25.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}割り切れない想いを力に変えてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:29.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無謀だと笑われた　何度も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:33.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}毎日が冒険で　青春で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:38.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい音と出会っては磨いてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:42.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}本気でやったからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:47.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こわい瞬間もあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:47.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}届けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:48.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:49.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:50.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:55.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一度息を吹き込む　明日へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:59.43,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}タクトに導かれてここまで来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:03.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたと来たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でているのは人生だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}響くのは感情だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:12.90,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと忘れないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.70,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}光る音が涙を照らしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:21.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}辛いことばかりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:26.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だっていつも　いつも楽しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:28.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そうでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:32.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！歌え　五線の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:39.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ヴィヴァーチェ！響け　遠くの春に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:25.44,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}青春的苦涩变为了前进的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:29.82,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}年少冲动让我无数次被嘲笑声掩埋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:33.66,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每天都在冒险　挥洒青春
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:38.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断磨练期待与新的乐声邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:42.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正因为全身心的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:47.13,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自然会有害怕的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:47.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要传递
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:48.84,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:49.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:50.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:55.30,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次向着奏响的明天迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:59.43,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵循指挥棒的指引来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:03.48,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正在奏响的是人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.86,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}余音缭绕的是情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:12.90,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都无法忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:16.70,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}耀眼的乐声将我们的泪水照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:21.16,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并非全是辛酸经历
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:26.68,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为　一路走来有许多快乐伴随着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:28.59,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:32.30,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！于五线谱之上唱响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:39.35,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}vivace！向着远处胜利的春天吹响吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------PART--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从今天这一刻起就是代表了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到竟然能去关西大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去全国吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和她们两个关系不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回吹奏部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L开始的极强音也要注意  不能让音色浑浊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鼓的鼓滚奏不要拖沓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今天的练习到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天开始就是盂兰盆假期了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但紧接着就是我们的集训
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定要当心身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请当心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要对集训的安排进行确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请各组长去平时的教室集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你盂兰盆节有什么安排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  没什么安排
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们一起去泳池吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你要不要我们一起去泳池…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  只是有些意外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为去年买的泳衣变得很紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想今年最后穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很紧…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入高中胸部就会变大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.66,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,720)\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}踌躇的长笛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是盂兰盆节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月游得真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年鼓起勇气买的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有点太成熟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  非常适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿我去买些果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边我已经占好位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我明年也能变大  穿上这样的泳衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就两个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月和小绿也一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真薄情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来这个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳池这种我也是会来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有今天能休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多人也来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美了  太美了  太美了  太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}等等  优子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织学姐真是太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是从天而降的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿的T恤怎么那么土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想被T恤上写着「水泥依存症」的人说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那上面写的还是「我的主食是爱」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要揪着上面的英语不放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是日本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先说这个的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来买冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其实是找的一个借口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际是从学姐她们哪里逃了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐们也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪学姐和优子学姐还是老样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子  冰淇淋买吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰淇淋还要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是吹悠风的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄前久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏纪也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有明日香学姐也在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就不去打扰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  你是竞赛会成员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年级的夏纪是后援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而一年级的你确实竞赛成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此你是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK\bord0\fs40\c&HD29C94&\pos(640,750)}绝对要拿金奖\N明年一起演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是无可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然北宇治的目标是全国大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就应该不论年级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吹得好的人去演奏才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北宇治  改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非得明日香学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是想回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找部长或者老师也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为明日香学姐是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐她  曾经阻止过我退部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我去年和三年级发生冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他人一起退出的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要退出啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那些无聊的家伙而留下痛苦的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种部待着也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说你蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些无聊的三年生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去管他们也马上就毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年就是我们自己说了算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能等到那时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回头想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候明日香学姐是想要挽留我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐今年是最后一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想要帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能一起演奏也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐知道那些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那她为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为不懂原因才难受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织学姐穿泳衣的样子简直是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有朋友要来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁那么善良做你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是希美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伞木希美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子和霙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两位都和你一样是南中吹奏部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点好奇为什么她们没有退部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子我和她提过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她说想再坚持看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那铠冢学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有和她提过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双簧管只有她一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也没有前辈对她说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上  她从一开始就是竞赛成员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么问这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面会不会有明日香学姐不同意你回来的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么希美学姐你想要回到部里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…也没有很奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢吹奏乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本想要努力练习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们的社团变为不输强校的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家都很害怕那些前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有试着去做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最后被无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得自己已经无能为力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无奈之下才退部的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今年  吹奏部却打进了关西大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显得我做的一切像个傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没这么觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我回来对这个部也没有益处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经和她说我哪里不好我会改  但还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟是哪里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我没放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望你不要再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  我去问她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不让你回来的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我去问她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心意我领了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些  你还不走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友在等着你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盂兰盆假期转眼就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天两夜的集训开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好宽敞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉能在这里得到不错的练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您那么早就已经到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给美知惠老师一个人来监督总觉得过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是平时练习您也总是很早就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这份工作值得我这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有妻子和儿女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作是我唯一可做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要说那种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  在练习开始之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想向大家介绍一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是从今天开始指导我们木管乐器的新山聪美老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新山聪美  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木管乐器？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷老师真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午木管乐器的同学去第二音乐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打击乐器和铜管乐器在这练习
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新山老师虽然年轻  但非常优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好遵从她的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优秀什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算夸我  我也没有好处给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我只是实话实说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能得到泷老师的称赞  我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况  什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是那种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那种关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那的是完全变成死鱼眼的丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小绿我最喜欢咖哩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分组练习辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有低音大提琴和木管乐器在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己被孤立了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新山老师怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  她是和泷老师一样严苛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会那样重复好几十次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实有像泷老师的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可难熬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该明白吧  总是这样说我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱说话只会起反效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你在泳池和希美她聊过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫我和你说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  让你不用特意去为她做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到去年的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不想因为自己给学妹添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很喜欢希美学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憧憬更为贴切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美是南中吹奏部的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和我相反  是个非常有耐心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是希美她过去耿直
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和去年的三年生发生了冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想以竞赛会为目标好好练习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而我非但没帮她  还说了不该说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她们说了也白说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙的性格就是渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着三年生的前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一冲动就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  算是赎罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让希美回到部里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我在她最痛苦的时候却什么都没为她做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  你现在的注意力应该放在关西大赛上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希美的事情我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然回答一句「知道了」很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这句话却一直在喉咙里没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我回来对这个部也没有益处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  算是赎罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让希美回到部里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐为什么不肯同意希美学姐回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是现在让她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰乱了部里的安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会对关西大赛造成影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得明日香学姐的判断是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这样说没错…但…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我心里对这件事根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁担任独奏什么的  只是件无聊透顶的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这个夏天就一直持续下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟哪个是她的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠冢学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放那首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐  你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不着  来打打音游
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音游不放声音也能打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你喜欢竞赛会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛结果都是由评审的喜好来决定的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这也是无可奈何的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可奈何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明会有很多人为此伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是竞赛会这种东西不存在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么铠冢学姐为什么还在坚持呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了高中我们一定要拿金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经完全搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得泷老师和新山老师在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定觉得年龄接近的比较适合他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事不问他本人是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  丽奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很成熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉我们明明同岁却完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是外表还是内在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿能占用你点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  下一首乐曲开始了
